{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/TakeABreath.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_InThroughTheNose.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to the Valley of Shadow.</strong> In it, you will experience a REAL harrowing journey of loss through the eyes of the developer. Experience the depth of grief as he visits the places of his childhood and discovers where love and acceptance come together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Header_ATrueStory_Cards.png?t=1730487672\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/TrueStory.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_A_Photo.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the dramatic retelling of a traumatic event in the lives of the developers, three siblings, through the eyes of one as he attempts to heal. REAL VHS tapes, photographs and answering machine audio piece together the fall and redemption of a once broken family.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Header_FantasySpells_Cards.png?t=1730487672\" /><br><br>Unlock some of the most iconic magical abilities from the fantasy genre as you make your way through the Valley and beyond: Light, Force Missile, and Fireball. Engage in increasingly complex challenges that require a mastery of each spell, both individually and in conjunction with the others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Light_Final1.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_TheresSomethingHere.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cast Light</strong> to not only find your way around dark areas, but also solve mind-bending puzzles revolving around Light &amp; Shadow. Strategically manipulate your environment to control the shadows indirectly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/ForceMissile.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_LetItMoveThroughYou.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Force Missiles</strong> always find their target, but <i>which</i> target is up to you. Destroy obstacles, manipulate the environment, and reposition yourself to control the route that your missiles take.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Fireball.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_ThisPlaceIsIceAndFire.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fireball</strong> opens new avenues to explore while you progress deeper into the icy cold Valley of Shadow. Carve through ice to make a path for Force Missile, or melt snow to shine Light on the other side.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Header_NostalgicMementos_Cards.png?t=1730487672\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Mementos.gif?t=1730487672\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/Quote_TheyreGames.png?t=1730487672\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Valley of Shadow is both a treasure and a tomb of nostalgia from the 80's, 90's and the 2000's. Each piece is significant, and each one familiar to the player. Some of the most popular pieces even have their own puzzles designed for them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1414030/extras/ThisBelongs.gif?t=1730487672\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Purgatorio...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/8e717066fdebf351ab3a8423062695854564248f.jpg"},{"name":"...Inferno...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/e72e423d9662b37f68b77326236f38ea29549d23.jpg"},{"name":"The first day of the rest of your life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/a77d72ceb5c17bc2dce43e4582d7e8e07bb34bf4.jpg"},{"name":"As Below, So Above","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/7da3b7d603c2259c41e31323b1f0f8f839631aa1.jpg"},{"name":"You can't keep fighting this alone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/be71a5636008ff8e5de5738d8e0f83157e468ddd.jpg"},{"name":"... where you can give us the love we need. ~ b.h.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/1984cd215ba67bd9ff0ed2785d4d23cf7764c9be.jpg"},{"name":"...Paradiso.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1414030/1e25a231d09157811e91dfdade544e4104fe6a8d.jpg"},